Eclipse has several useful XML editing and validation tools. This video shows you how to use these tools and validate an XML document with a DTD document.

This is part of the online course, Web Services, offered by Computer Careers at South Central College, North Mankato, MN 56003 USA. http://cc.southCentral.edu

